==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ʌvəl|-ʌvəl]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
{{wikipedia}}
# A hand tool with a handle for moving portions of material such as earth, snow, grain, etc from one place to another.  Not to be confused with a [[spade]] which is for [[digging]].
# {{US}} A spade.

